data.description: In the heart of Uvalde, stands a completely remodeled modern bungalow. Inside you will find a house suited to families and entertaining.  With four spacious light-filled bedrooms and 3 full baths, this house checks all the boxes.  The master suite tile work is stunning and the closet provides ample space for you and your spouse. With a total of 2,300 sq feet there is room to relax and enjoy. The kitchen is spacious and includes lux finishes. It also provides loads of cabinets and includes a large pantry. The outdoor entertainment area is beautiful day or night with a custom crafted rock-wall fountain and outdoor kitchen. You have over 2 acres to enjoy the hill country views, a quaint green house, multiple outbuildings for your lawn equipment and hobbies, and a convenient irrigation system.  It's a gardeners dream and ready for your family's move-in now.
